QuestData.Title: Olemba Seed Oil
QuestData.Description: The oily seeds from the forest's olemba trees could prove very valuable. I'd like to gather a larger quantity of them, press them for their oil, and then see what I can do with it.$B$BJust think, there's a whole forest full of trees out there, producing a lot of seeds that go to waste. I don't care if it turns out to be cooking oil, lamp oil, or weapon oil, I won't let it go to waste!$B$BBring me any of the seeds that you happen to gather from the olemba cones. They're all over the place.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring 30 Olemba Seeds to Rakoria in Stonebreaker Hold.
QuestData.CompletionText: Do you have any seeds for me?
QuestData.RewardText: That's a good start, but we're going to need more than that if we're to press a respectable amount of oil!
